This package accepts a dataset 'data' with a dependant variable y and a set of independant X {x:x is a categorical/numeric variable}

The package is to:
Return a dataset data_cat with y and categorical (all numeric fields converted to bins) X
Test for each X IV, WoE and significance against y
Reduces the set of X as per user defined IV and WoE Cut-Offs
Plot the WoE trends for user/package selected variables
